msg: On the fs-successor-ids branch: Bump the FS-BDB format number to 5, and make
the "successor ids" table conditional on format number at least 5.
Also fix an unrelated test that failed if password stores were not configured
(open_databases): Make opening the successor ids database conditional.
the use of the successor ids table conditional.
if the format is less than 5.
(svn_fs_base__delete_node_revision): Fix a typo in the doc string.
(timestamp_behaviour): Add an empty "password-stores =" option in the config
file, to prevent the test from seeing a warning message generated by
failing to load a Gnome Keyring authentication library. This is the same
solution used by other tests that create their own config file.
